Task 3 : Cat commands
1. touch umuzi.txt
   touch recruit.txt
   touch cohort.txt
2. nano umuzi.txt
   nano recruit.txt
   nano cohort.txt
3. cat umuzi.txt recruit.txt cohort.txt
4. cat umuzi.txt recruit.txt cohort.txt > summary.txt
5. cat >> summary.txt (Enter then Control d)

Task 4 : The locate command
1. locate umuzi.txt
2. locate umuzi.txt > search_result.txt

Task 5 The locate command cont..
1.mkdir mydocument
 cd mydocument
 touch pad.txt
2. cd Desktop
   mkdir work
3.cp /Desktop/mydocument/pad.txt pad_copy.txt  
4. locate updatedb
5. cd ..
6. locate pad_copy.txt

Task 6 Find commands
1. find . -type f -iname *.pdf
2. find . -type f -iname *.pdf > work
3. find . -mtime -1 -print

    

